decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing a variety of different colored cards to quickly overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures and burn spells. By efficiently utilizing mana fixing and powerful multicolor cards, the deck aims to consistently put pressure on the opponent while also disrupting their game plan with cards like Stubborn Denial and Leyline Binding. Additionally, the inclusion of versatile creatures like Ragavan, Nimble Pilferer and Scion of Draco helps ensure the deck has both a strong early game presence and the ability to close out the game quickly.

The deck focuses on quickly generating mana through rituals and medallions to cast a high number of spells in a single turn. It utilizes cards like Wrenn's Resolve and Ral, Monsoon Mage to draw cards and filter through the deck for combo pieces. The deck aims to assemble the combo pieces to generate a large storm count and finish the game with cards like Grapeshot. The deck also includes cards like Valakut Awakening and Wish to manipulate the hand and find specific cards needed for the combo.
